INSTALLATION / BUILDING instructions:

*) Uncompress archive
    tar zxvf playwm_latest.tgz
*) Go to extracted directory
    cd playwm-0.2
*) Compile 
    make
*) Install (as a root)
    make install
*) Install depending software: feh, xcompmgr, tint2, volumeicon-alsa, openbox, menu, rxvt-unicode, xfonts-terminus
   This step is system depending.

*) Log out and select new menu entry in display manager login window, or call "playwm" in your startx file. 
 
 
